title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable Plaiting Materials & Veg. Prds. Nie
description: Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable Plaiting Materials & Veg. Prds. Nie in the United Kingdom decreased to 0.57 GBP Million in September from 0.70 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Vegetable Plaiting Materials & in the United Kingdom averaged 0.49 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 3.43 GBP Million in November of 2021 and a record low of 0 GBP Million in December of 1999. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Vegetable Plaiting Material.
